{"tid":1222940,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"我想問 依d牛真係正常？","createTime":"2019-06-14T14:51:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T07:23:52.000Z","uid":237555,"like":1,"dislike":48,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"11030b998de41ec07cf671df5f2e3acdce527b9d","tid":1222940,"uid":237555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T14:51:43.000Z","msg":"依加係堅韓牛 韓燒火鍋雙放題 (旺角)<br />\n旺角彌敦道726號16樓<br />\n第一輪叫野食望一望d牛咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qcn6743.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQcn6743.png&h=d21242f5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ofdNSwM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FofdNSwM.png&h=876fa36f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bGF8BYu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbGF8BYu.png&h=689767bc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ycr7SwS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fycr7SwS.png&h=0b4b60d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n岩岩我叫個經理黎 <br />\n我話我成餐點食？<br />\n食壞人都似<br />\n諗住叫佢免左佢算 <br />\n去第間食<br />\n點知個經理話無問題係正常 個態度仲要勁串<br />\n依加我call 左食環黎<br />\n除左依樣仲可以點樣比多d人知道e間野d野咁<br />\n廢事害人?<br />\n<br />\n(已經叫佢個放題278+1)"},{"pid":"df976648d02eda629c6d532e1bd79cd9e4da0673","tid":1222940,"uid":237555,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T14:53:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4a79cb55ebc0ef0916dec776b3239a5cde4ce344","tid":1222940,"uid":75050,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T14:54:57.000Z","msg":"報食環，話自己食完屙到仆街，食環會去查架啦"},{"pid":"0e77bb3a911ff2cae0b8c5617dcd8ae4da69e7f3","tid":1222940,"uid":75050,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4a79cb55ebc0ef0916dec776b3239a5cde4ce344","tid":1222940,"uid":75050,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T14:54:57.000Z","msg":"報食環，話自己食完屙到仆街，食環會去查架啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T14:55:35.000Z","msg":"不過如果查完無問題即係你柒